oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Military Report, SSU 558
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Military report providing a summary of the services of SSU 558.The report was issued in late December of 1918. Page 1 provides a summary of SSU 558 from June 1917 to April 1918. Page 2 provides a summary of SSU 558 from May 1918 to November 1918. Page 3 offers concluding remarks about the services of SSU 558. There is a note attached to the page, which is written in French.
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:source: Robert Frank Hodge World War I Papers, 1914-1919
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:subject: American Field Service; World War, 1914-1918
Military report
